closeWithoutChangingDescription.value: Close without changing with Escape key.

pauseOrPlayActionDescription.value: Pause or play action with alt key plus K.

adjustFaucetFlowDescription.value: Adjust faucet flow with Left and Right Arrow keys.

openFaucetFullyDescription.value: Open faucet fully with End key.

openFaucetBrieflyDescription.value: Open faucet briefly with Space or Enter keys.

simSpeedDescription.value: For closer observations Play sim on slower speed.
